column4: hey guys, i'm new to ubuntu. i just successfully installed photoshop cs5 with wine, now i need to install dreamweaver. could anybody help me out here? the photoshop installer was modified so you didn't need wine tricks, but the dreamweaver installer didn't work.
Please go to #winehq -- we don't support Windows apps here.
Server? Why are you running wine on the server edition? That hardly makes sense
Err... you need to type "/join #winehq" (without quotes). You'll also need to register, likely.
